Package org.anchoranalysis.image.channel.convert

Converts a channel to other data-types.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChannelConverter<T>
    Converts a channel from one type to another specific type.
    ChannelConverterMulti
    Converts a channel from one type to multiple other types.
    ToFloat  
    ToUnsignedByte
    Converts from other data types to UnsignedByteBuffer (unsigned 8-bit) without scaling.
    ToUnsignedByteScaleByMinMaxValue
    Converts from other data types to UnsignedByteBuffer (unsigned 8-bit) scaling from the range of the source data-type.
    ToUnsignedShort

    ConversionPolicy
